175
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:30,270
Hi, I'm Monica. And this is Chandler.
我叫莫妮卡, 这是钱德

176
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:32,670
-Please come in. -Thank you.
-请进！ -谢谢

177
00:12:32,850 --> 00:12:35,980
