That's the last time Emma is getting on one of those things for her entire life.
算了, 这辈子再也不许艾玛接近它

209
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:51,210
No, no, no. Okay, it wasn't the swing's fault. It was my fault.
别这样, 不是秋千的错, 是我错

