-All right, fine. I'll do it. -Good.
-好!谁怕谁 -好！

219
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:27,310
-If you hold a spider. -Where?! Where?!
-如果你敢抓蜘蛛 -在哪儿?

220
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:30,420
If you hold a spider.
我说"如果"你敢抓蜘蛛

