00:15:30,590 --> 00:15:32,290
I know.
听见了

222
00:15:39,370 --> 00:15:42,730
Guys, is everything okay? It's me, Joey.
没事吧? 是我, 乔伊--

223
00:15:44,940 --> 00:15:46,630
Adoption!
领养!

224
00:15:48,410 --> 00:15:49,710
What's going on?
到底什么事?

225
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:52,470
Oh, it's just like I said, that crazy..
就是那个疯子...

226
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:56,170
Bert, roaming the halls.
叫bert的 在过道上跑

227
00:15:56,350 --> 00:15:59,480
-Guys? -Keep on roaming, Bert!
-嗨！ -bert, 接着跑

228
