We don't want any crazy today!
今天我们不看你疯了

229
00:16:03,990 --> 00:16:05,960
Is he all right out there by himself?
他独自一个在外面，不会出事吧?

230
00:16:06,130 --> 00:16:09,460
Oh, yeah. He has a caretaker. His older brother..
没事, 他哥照顾他

231
