-Bert 和 Ernie? (芝麻街的动画角色)? -无巧不成书

233
00:16:19,470 --> 00:16:23,380
-What's going on? -We'll talk later! Everything's fine!
-怎么了？ -我们等会再说，一切都好！

234
00:16:24,110 --> 00:16:26,670
Everything doesn't sound fine.
听起来一切都不好！

235
00:16:35,990 --> 00:16:38,890
Bert and Ernie have a big yellow bird.
Bert 和 Ernie 有一只大黄鸟！

236
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:44,960
You never told me about that guy and your sweet 16.
你没说过你16岁时被男人追杀的故事

237
00:16:45,130 --> 00:16:47,600
-I'm sorry about that. -Oh, it ended okay.
-真可怜 -结局还算好

238
00:16:47,770 --> 00:16:49,740
One of my friends shot him.
我朋友毙了他

239
00:16:51,540 --> 00:16:55,070
At least you'll get a proper wedding. You really deserve that.
至少你会有个体面婚礼, 你该得的

240
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:59,180
Yeah, I really do. You know, I had nothing growing up.
没错, 我这辈子还没风光过

241
00:17:01,650 --> 00:17:03,980
Just like the kids I took the money from.
就像被我剥夺金钱的那些孩子一样

242
00:17:04,150 --> 00:17:08,990
No. No, no. I see where this is going. Don't make me go back there.
看出你苗头了, 别又想让我退回去

243
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:11,950
I'm sorry, but I want to regive the money to the children.
抱歉, 但我又想把钱给孩子们了

244
00:17:12,130 --> 00:17:16,320
But we can't. I mean, you called that guy a sweaty little man.
但是我们不能, 我是说 你管那男人叫流汗男

245
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:19,720
Unless you were talking about me. We never really cleared that up.
除非你在说我 我们从没真正弄干净过

246
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:24,300
Look, I can't have a wedding with this money now. It's tainted.
我不能用这钱办婚事, 这不道德

247
00:17:25,410 --> 00:17:26,930
Fine, we'll give the money back.
好吧, 退回去作数

248
00:17:27,110 --> 00:17:29,540
If that guy at the charity gives us a hard time..
如果慈善捐助处那家伙又叫咱们难看

249
00:17:29,710 --> 00:17:33,040
my friend hasn't shot anyone in a really long time.
我朋友的老枪好久没见过血了

250
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:38,370
I must say this seems like a lovely environment to raise a child in.
我想说, 这个家庭培养小孩似乎很理想

251
00:17:38,550 --> 00:17:41,450
You are welcome to look under any of the furniture..
你尽可以在各种家具下面搜查

252
00:17:41,620 --> 00:17:45,110
because, believe me, you won't find any porn or cigarettes under there.
绝无色情书刊和香烟什么的!

253
00:17:46,190 --> 00:17:50,690
Before we look around, let me make sure I have everything I need up to here.
在到处看看之前, 要问你们一些问题

254
00:17:56,470 --> 00:17:59,000
Why don't I show you the baby's room.
带你看看婴儿房

255
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:05,870
