-你干啥? -你不让我进来

256
00:18:06,050 --> 00:18:08,340
-I thought you were in trouble. -Well, we're not.
-我以为你们出事了 -才没有!

257
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:10,810
But you called me "Bert."
但你叫我"bert", 

258
00:18:11,450 --> 00:18:13,480
That's our code word for danger.
那是"危险"的暗号

259
00:18:14,590 --> 00:18:18,580
-We don't have a code word. -We don't?
-我们没约定过什么暗号 -是吗？ 

260
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:20,490
We really should.
应该约一个

261
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:24,600
From now on, "Bert" will be our code word for danger.
从今往后，"bert"就用来作为 遇到危险的暗号

262
00:18:24,770 --> 00:18:27,360
So that was the baby's room.
参观完婴儿房

263
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:33,470
-What room should we see next? -Any room that isn't behind this couch.
-下面参观哪里？ -除了沙发下面都可以参观！

264
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:39,140
Some people don't get him, but I think he's really funny.
有些人不懂他的笑话 但我觉得他真幽默

265
00:18:46,150 --> 00:18:48,820
I did not care for that.
我不在乎被你粗暴对待

266
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:50,820
You have to leave.
你得回避

267
00:18:50,990 --> 00:18:53,720
You slept with our social worker and never called her back.
你和这个社工睡过，再没联络她

268
00:18:53,890 --> 00:18:55,920
She is still pissed, so she can't see you.
她还在生你的气，不能让她见你

269
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:57,930
Okay, okay.
好，好，好！我躲起来

270
00:19:00,830 --> 00:19:03,670
-What? -I forgot my bat.
-怎么了？ -忘了拿球棒

271
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:08,340
Oh, my God.
天！

272
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:12,710
And for the last time, we do not want to be friends with you!
最后警告，我们不想和你做朋友！

273
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:17,950
And we don't wanna buy your bat!
也不想买你的球棒！

274
00:19:19,290 --> 00:19:21,050
What are you doing here?
你在这儿干什么？

275
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:23,990
Bert. Bert. Bert. Bert.
Bert. Bert. Bert. Bert.

276
00:19:27,630 --> 00:19:31,090
-Are you friends with him? -I can explain.
-你们是朋友？ -我来解释

277
