你漂亮，聪明，有趣

291
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:26,920
We had a really good time.
咱们春风一度

292
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:31,020
If I had your number, why wouldn't I call you?
如果我有你电话，怎么可能不打给你？

293
00:20:31,690 --> 00:20:32,750
I don't know.
我就是不知道呀

294
00:20:35,130 --> 00:20:37,150
Well, maybe I'm wrong. I'm sorry.
可能我搞错了，对不起

295
00:20:37,330 --> 00:20:42,200
Hey, too late for apologies. Okay? You broke my heart.
现在道歉太晚啦 你伤了我的心

296
00:20:42,370 --> 00:20:45,900
You know how many women I had to sleep with to get over you?
就为了忘掉你，我睡了多少女人啊！

297
00:20:48,980 --> 00:20:51,070
-Joey, wait.. -No!
-乔伊，等等 -不！

298
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:54,210
I waited a long time! I can't wait anymore.
我等得够久，不可能再等了

299
00:20:57,750 --> 00:21:00,650
I'm sorry that you had to see that. I'm so embarrassed.
抱歉让你们笑话了，真尴尬

300
00:21:00,820 --> 00:21:04,090
-Oh, that's really okay. -Yeah. We totally understand.
-没事， -我们理解

301
00:21:04,260 --> 00:21:07,850
-Dating is hard. -Boy, you people are nice.
-约会可够人受的 -你们真是好人

302
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:11,390
And I've got to say..
我得说…

303
00:21:11,570 --> 00:21:15,330
I think you're going to make excellent parents.
你们一定会是很棒的父母

304
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:20,240
Laura!
劳拉！

305
00:21:27,350 --> 00:21:29,140
We're back.
我们回来啦

306
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:32,280
Are you here to take more money?
还想要钱

